title: Register to book driving tests for your pupils

heading_context: Register to book driving tests for your pupils
chunks.html_content:
You cannot currently register to book driving tests for your pupils online.

Email the Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (DVSA) if you need to register to book driving tests.

Use the subject title ‘Register to book driving tests’.

You need to include your:

  • full name
  • address and postcode
  • date of birth
  • telephone number
  • approved driving instructor (ADI) personal reference number

customerservices@dvsa.gov.uk

heading_context: Register to book driving tests for your pupils
chunks.html_content:
You can still book tests for your pupils using the public booking service without registering.

You can apply to book theory tests for your pupils, check or change appointments or cancel test appointments if you’re an instructor or trainer.

You must have already registered with DVSA to book driving tests before you apply.
